<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title || 'About - Express Quiz App' %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/output.css" />
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen min-w-screen overflow-x-clip">
    <div class="main min-h-screen w-screen bg-background bg-image">
        <!-- Reused Navigation from index.ejs (Simplified) -->
        <nav id="main-nav" class="p-4 gap-2 flex justify-center fixed w-full top-0 z-50">
            <nav class="glint bg-primary/50 text-purple-300 flex justify-evenly items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full w-[60%] backdrop-blur-xl">
                <a href="/" class="glint text-3xl font-ramen px-4 py-2 bg-primary rounded-full translate-y-[2px] shadow-lg">SHITSUMON</a>
                <div class="flex gap-4 items-center h-full">
                    <a href="/shop" class="font-poppins hover:text-pink-400 transition-colors">SHOP</a>
                    <a href="/about" class="font-poppins text-pink-400 border-b border-pink-400">ABOUT</a>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="flex w-full min-h-screen pt-24 px-8 justify-center items-center">
            <div class="glint bg-primary/80 backdrop-blur-xl p-8 rounded-3xl border border-purple-300/20 max-w-2xl text-purple-300 font-poppins shadow-2xl">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-ramen text-center text-purple-300 mb-6 tracking-wider">About This App</h1>
                <p class="text-lg mb-4 text-purple-300/90">
                    This is a custom Express.js quiz application built with Node.js, EJS templates, and an integrated PHP backend for authentication.
                </p>
                <div class="bg-purple-950/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-purple-300/10 mb-6">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-pink-400">Architecture</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-purple-300/80">
                        <li>Routes defined in <code>routes/quiz.js</code> and <code>routes/pages.js</code></li>
                        <li>API logic in <code>controllers/quizController.js</code></li>
                        <li>Dynamic styling via <b>Tailwind CSS v4</b> and <b>DaisyUI</b></li>
                        <li>PHP Bridge used for secure local database communication</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
                    <a href="/" class="glint bg-primary px-8 py-3 font-ramen text-2xl text-purple-300 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary/80 transition-all shadow-md">
                        <span class="translate-y-[2px]">Return Home</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>